    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Your Kids Are Their Problem</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Communitarian Network director Amitai Etzioni letter notes that child-free people described in Lisa Belkin's July 23 article are selfish in their use of free time</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>None of the child-free people in your article reported that they use their time, energy and resources for any purpose other than self. It is their quiet time with a glass of wine that children threatened; children did not crimp their style, say, for working as Doctors Without Borders or in soup kitchens.</p>
        <p>Amitai Etzioni  Director  The Communitarian Network  Washington</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
